column5: Figure I'm up at Lew o'clock... may as well say good morning for once!  Have a great week folks... be back in a few days. Off to St. Mike's a go to sit in a waiting lounge all day.  Wayne
Top of the Marning to Ya too. Bring snacks, a book, maybe tie some flies... Have a great day
Hug Jennifer, Wayne. Catch you in a few days. You and Leah be well and trust the people who are looking after Jen.
Mornin Wayne, best of luck to your daughter today Bud, St. Mikes is a good place.  We'll probably be passing each other on the 400, I'm delivering a car to Barrie this morning.
Morning all! Played the waiting game many times myself with Sue. The waiting is always the hardest part. take along some good fishing magazines.
we wish her well...our thoughts are with you
This one time eh   Seriously Wayne I hope all goes well for your daughter today.
Same here Wayne, I hope all goes well.
Mornin' Wayne....our thoughts are with your daughter!!..
You have our phone numbers Wayne....give us a shout if you need anything!  Hope all goes well today.
We hope all goes well Wayne...She is in a good hospital...  Both Maribeth and I were born in St. Mike's...We think that's good !!!
Hey Wayne, tried to stop in and see you guys, but I was running late both times I was there   Hope all went well  Maureen
